descrShort: Number of requests (excluding the retransmission messages)
Number of responses (excluding the retransmission messages)
Time between the request and the responses in seconds
Time between the request sending and the receiving of the same request in seconds
Time between the response sending and the receiving of the same response in seconds
Number/percentage of requests retransmissions (excluding the initial message)
Number/percentage of response retransmissions (excluding the initial message)
